Sinew can be used on a spinning wheel by a member with 10 Crafting to create crossbow string, granting 15 Crafting experience. It is created through the Cooking skill, by using a piece of raw beef (not of the undead kind) or bear meat with a range and choosing to make sinew, granting 3 Cooking experience.

Sinew can also be created by using a knife on a damaged monkey tail, requiring 10 Crafting.
